TearOffBay class    @{"Index" link "Classes.guide/Main"} @{"Super" link "GroupClass.guide/Main"}
@{u}                                                             @{uu}

  @{fg text}Warning@{fg text}: current public releases of TearOffbay.mcc and
  TearOffPanel.mcc are very bugged. They crash very easily.
  TearOffbay.rxmec and TearOffPanel.rxmec are in the official
  RxMUI distribution only with the hope a fixed versions of the
  MCCs comes out.

  The TearOffBay class creates groups to handle TearOffPanels.

  TearOffBay class is a subclass of TearOffBay.mcc, so you must
  have TearOffBay.mcc in MUI:Libs/mui/ to use it. TearOffBay.mcc
  is copyright of Szymon Ulatowski.

